quests.desc: Welcome to another fast paced round of TextWorld! Here is how to play! Your first objective is to make an attempt to move west. After that, attempt to head west. And then, head north. With that over with, head east. And then, make an effort to go east. And then, take a trip north. Then, attempt to move north. With that over with, make an attempt to move west. And then, pick up the cuboid key from the floor of the shower. If you can get your hands on the cuboid key, check that the cuboid locker within the shower is unlocked with the cuboid key. Once that's all handled, you can stop!
commands: unlock cuboid locker with cuboid key

walkthrough: unlock cuboid locker with cuboid key

objective: Who's got a virtual machine and is about to play through an profound round of TextWorld? You do! First step, venture west. And then, venture west. After that, attempt to move north. That done, travel east. After that, try to travel east. Once you get through with that, travel north. And then, make an effort to go north. Once you get through with that, go west. And then, pick-up the cuboid key from the floor of the shower. After that, unlock the cuboid locker with the cuboid key. Got that? Good!
